1 be counted. If a voter was properly registered to vote in the election by the
2 county board, no mistake of an election official in giving the voter a ballot or
3 in failing to comply with G.S. 163-82.15 or G.S. 163-166.11 shall serve to
4 prevent the counting of the vote on any ballot item the voter was eligible by
