6 (5) Precinct officials shall provide a preliminary report of the vote counting on
7 election day to the county board of elections as quickly as possible. The
8 preliminary report shall be unofficial, has shall:
9 a. Be unofficial.
10 b. Have no binding effect upon the official county canvass to follow, and
